
Common packaging and distribution
---------------------------------


Stand-alone
-----------

Just works as a standa-alone application.


Debian Lenny
------------
cat 'deb http://rep.logentries.com/ lenny main' > /etc/apt/sources.list.d/logentries.list
gpg --keyserver php.mit.edu --recv-keys C43C79AD && gpg -a --export C43C79AD | apt-key add -
aptitude update
aptitude install logentries


Debian Squeeze
--------------
cat 'deb http://rep.logentries.com/ squeeze main' > /etc/apt/sources.list.d/logentries.list
gpg --keyserver php.mit.edu --recv-keys C43C79AD && gpg -a --export C43C79AD | apt-key add -
aptitude update
aptitude install logentries

